cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper proposes a new neural network structure for defending against adversarial attacks. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-categories. Among these, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories as the paper focuses on the neural network structure and its theoretical and empirical analysis.
